Sometimes things blow up and out of proportion so that you can understand the need for distance… time and space allow for more understanding, just don’t disregard your newly found perspective ever .

Tore my ACL… so no more physical activity, 🙃using this as an opportunity to dive back into my artwork . 
I’m not as bummed as I would have thought myself to be… a lil frustrated but quite a few things from my life have prepared me to transmute the feelings I have into other things… like creativity . 

Thankful for all the well wishes and prayers… just yesterday I was reverse clutching, hitting casual 360s, and self-alley oops .

And you thought I was introspective before 🌞 🙂 . 
Time to pivot and figure out how to scale the brand and make a few more things make sense .

In pursuit of peak performance, just within reach . 

Opportunity as options are something you seek …

The conversations I have, and even how they are contextualized are exactly what I’ve dreamed of . The understanding I didn’t know existed . The Full range of emotions . Never afraid to feel, never afraid to heal . Submission in the entry sense isn’t possible without it’s other context .  So…What do you wanna do ? Something I continually ask myself and hear from others, listening to their response and qualifying the interaction .

Material wealth means nothing in the absence of health, peace, and I guess the word would be “prosperity”… and for some reason that word is not synonymous with success, and more closely related to the longevity of such .

I’ve grown so much in my expression that it’s hard to understand why it gets or ever is so hard, of course I take inspiration from famous faces, but I’ve also been more inspired by some of the folks I’ve met on this journey . That way I know I’m pulling from what’s real and authentic to my own experience… 
“Lyrics”, Melodie’s, and rhythms I’ve felt internally I finally have the confidence to let out . 

If I told you what I was pursuing you’d be like… fr ? 
Cuz it’s not an award, it’s not even the bread fr . It’s fully expressing the person that walks around everyday, interacting with the world around me . Stop rushing, who told you it would be fast… or easy… or even fun ? That’s all relative to how you take things on anyway . 
****huge shoutout to @prolificyouafool of course ***

I never understood the obsession with Prince… til I grew up and realized he had people convinced… 
He was the smoothest … I mean smooth fr . 
He had me singing for her kisses, purple rain no schpielssss…

I think one of the most disheartening feelings as a creative is the fear of over saturation . Not necessarily of a single thing you are creating, but questions of whether not you’re doing anything special, or different enough to stand out . While my “content” may be reaching however many thousands of people… how many people is my ART touching ? And why do they want it over, or in addition to others ? It’s really remarkable to try and understand… and I really don’t know any true numbers or metrics to measure… however given the opportunity I’ll always take the time to ask someone what makes them purchase… because if they have an answer I can possibly fit them into something or atleast be better versed for the next opportunity to sell . The realization of this commodified world is either you want something or not . And once you get past that painfully freeing wall of acceptance, things go pretty smooth . Maybe not financially, or physically (🩼🩼) INITIALLY lol but It’s something to deal with on the daily and do your best at . 
I find it key to keep people who encourage me through my lows and keep me close to them during my highs . People who remind of what I’ve done, what I’m capable of, where I’ve been, and how all of it both matters and doesn’t matter at all … It’s kinda dark to think but… my only other option would be to give up everything… and sincerely I don’t even feel I’m capable of doing that . So call it positive thinking, or good vibrations, and whatever you may… but my focus is forward and not necessarily always in the directional sense…but always in a progressive sense .
I’ve met many people who have been interested and even enamored by my talents… my drive… my ambition, and my creativity, and previously I was so anxious about getting a return I cut myself off from a lot of possible interactions and opportunities . To arrive here again thinking about what the people I meet are in pursuit of . What does that look like to them ? Where do they believe they find it if they don’t have it already… ? If it’s sitting/standing across from them… And where is the rush ?
Nail of Thumb…

These are like love notes 🥲. To myself . And my extended family ? 

This injury makes me feel more broken than I’ve ever felt before . Reminders to “hang in there” and I’m like where bro …hang in where ? 

Running out of patience faster than you could ever run out of money 😂 . 

You think it’s about the lines… it’s not . 
It’s about the start… and the ability to continue . Sharpie on Cardboard Pizza Boxes so far feels exactly like crutches… it’s like I’m heartbroken, and every ounce of inspiration goes into making my next move LITERALLY . Supposed to be still, but the angst and pressure that doing “nothing” from my surroundings hits different . 

I choose to be direct… because why would you not choose the shortest distance when you on crutches lol . 

It cost more to make a pizza box than it does for the paper you’d see any traditional art on… but no point in doing math or anything like that . Your associations with value is skewed by the inability to re-contextualize .

 Lol when’s the last time you spent $18-$30 for 2 pieces of paper ?

The simplicity I’ve found, by searching around my town afforded me with the  opportunities to find my sound . 
Deep thought, we drown it out . We fought, figured it out . Why there so many people who’d do anything for some clout .
Swimmin with the sharks taught me never hold ya breath . If ya breathing believe it as if it’s written on ya chest . If I give it my all I’m expecting nothing less . Count up every single way it’s bulletproof if you invest . 
I’m like the undercurrent- long before you find the flow . I could show you so many different plays X’s and O’s . I can’t be the only person that would ever tell you no . Way too privileged with perception to ever hit on the nose . 
Expression is the intersection of memory and articulation . So… safe to say you telling me it never happened no longer suffices. Drown that out .

I’m really into world building . So like… my understanding of line is so closely related to my understanding of weight, that they inform each other . And in majority of my pieces-no matter what I create- the lines are having conversations with the weight 😭 and I love it . 
I’m drawing right now because I know I’m pretty good at it . “Who gon tell me this cardboard is trash and really mean it with they chest out ?”
And you might as well forgive me before it’s too late .

The identity I’ve found by pushing and pulling together lines that would otherwise possibly never intersect, has left me little to no respect… for those who won’t simply take the time to engage or feel the need to voice an opinion without a basis of study, and rather solely rooted only on feeling . 

While all that means I did my job effectively . Let’s say time and time again .

My goals for range of motion are not only to get back on the court . I miss the yoga flow . The tai-chi, the kickboxing… shoot… THE MURALS lol So yeah I’m taking it a lil more serious to push way beyond between the leg dunking again . 

The day I’m cleared for weight bearing I’ll be hittin some ACL specific yoga-some **do not try this @ home** focused on strengthening my leg-and specifically my quads

Personified .

Last time I was here I was 8 years old . 
Felt like landing back on Earth .

I like the freedom associated with peace . Pieces of art and pieces like these, testing my balance and testing my knees . Blessing my balance no stressing the fees .
Walk around the city like I’m new here . Seeing faces that I know but never knew here . Plant the seed, watch the growth, see I grew here… your two eyes, they might cry more than two tears . I went to school I left the city left a few peers . And if im honest it’s behind us quite few years . So If you catch me slick rewinding bring me two beers . Hear me vibing on this timing through your two ears . 
My story crafted, by action, and limitless passion . Make em throw they hands in the air, before you mash it . Dropped my bike 2or3 times after I crashed it . Hot potato flew round my room, and so I smashed it . Every check you seen on physique, you could cash in . Spoiled by the people I meet, that’s how it happens . Maybe I’m just way too unique, and old fashioned…crazy when you watching you my feet, looks like I’m splashin
I been finding pictures wish I never would have posted . Toggling the throttle proof I’ve really been coasting
It’s true isn’t it
These digital will go crazy . I just haven’t had the digital vibes

What is it you’d give to revisit or relive ? 
Hopefully it’s nothing cuz you did what you just did . 
Hope you never lying in the sense of telling fibs . 
If God gave me a woman hope she came right from my ribs . 
How you get Eve in the. garden of Eden ?  Apples that we eating… aren’t even in season . 
I’m looking for the reasons, to get it through my evenings… so when I shine my light  it’s like more of a beacon . 
(Yal don’t really hear me tho)

I’m making Poetry that bleeds . ”I cant’s” replaced with ease. Grow plants that market tease . . Fulfillment of every need . My brand belongs on tees way more than B to C’s .
Somehow still picking cotton, as I’m pulling this weed .

I thought if I kept pushing life would open up for me . 
And that’s exactly how it works

I don’t mind that you don’t pay attention . The assumption that that is what made my sh*t HOT is what pigeonholed me previously . 
Ain’t no engagement-or the lack thereof ever made what I make… because I make what I make . 
Simultaneously I miss what I miss . 
The city I learned to claim . The state of mind that taps me in and out of whatever pushes this entire process forward . As much as I wish sitting still made it stop or slow down… it kinda just speeds it up . 
I wish for deep connection in my pursuit of happiness-reflections that teach me more of what they mean to me . Instead of me having to be the curious Matt I used to be . 
Flow until you know . Then flow some more . This the most uncomfortable I’ve been in my life . And it’s not from the growing pains as much as it is from the healing . 
I can’t get what’s for me if I’m not in position or properly prepared . 
To family . Extended and digitally adopted .  Push through . I’m w you .

MAY 21- I tore my ACL,MCL, PCL and meniscus hooping . Doc said a grenade blew up in my knee . 
JUNE 22- I had surgery to repair my entire knee . 

This has been the hardest year of my life Physically . Emotionally . Mentally . Spiritually . Artistically . Fiscally . And Creatively … it’s not that I didn’t want to work on anything, there have been so many blocks it’s not even funny . But at the same time it’s been the most growth I could quantify ever . When you go from 360 windmilling to learning to walk again . Your confidence is shot . 

When you go from basically jumping from the free throw line to your loved ones having to help you get around the house… your self-worth is more than fragile . 
I wouldn’t wish this on anyone who doesn’t also understand how strong you end up on the other side . 
Things I’m faced with now brush over easier than the fade I owe some of you for playing with my name . 
I wish myself and my family no more strife than God has for me to body every time to level up, over and over again . And always if you see me in the streets holl@ 
cuz when they tell me where it is a don’t belong I’ll show you atleast 5 ways where they wrong .

Do you not touch life with your paintbrush ? Everyday and Every night . 
If not, I do feel very sorry for the eyes who do not behold .
Feel like Anakin . But you would have to know where I started this whole thing 🐏↔️🔵😈
